WEBVTT

00:12.840 --> 00:13.560
Your Highness

00:17.960 --> 00:19.160
My men will follow all the way

00:20.160 --> 00:21.160
No one can mistreat you

00:21.880 --> 00:22.480
Teacher Yu

00:23.160 --> 00:23.920
Some things

00:25.240 --> 00:26.320
Hear but don't take to heart

00:27.440 --> 00:28.240
As long as one lives

00:29.280 --> 00:30.200
That's what matters most

00:31.280 --> 00:32.280
This subject

00:33.400 --> 00:35.640
Has brought trouble upon Your Highness

00:41.360 --> 00:42.320
I hope Teacher Yu

00:44.280 --> 00:44.920
Will take care

00:51.400 --> 00:52.840
Your Highness, take care

01:32.480 --> 01:33.080
What are you doing?

01:40.240 --> 01:41.080
Your students

01:42.160 --> 01:44.360
Thank Your Highness for your grace

01:45.000 --> 01:46.640
Thank you, Your Highness

01:46.840 --> 01:48.800
For protecting our teacher's life

01:51.800 --> 01:53.240
If there is an opportunity in the future

01:54.120 --> 01:55.440
We will repay Your Highness's great kindness

01:57.160 --> 01:57.800
Enough

01:58.800 --> 02:00.600
You are all pillars of Great Xuan's future

02:03.120 --> 02:03.800
Rise quickly

02:04.840 --> 02:05.680
All of you, rise

02:09.360 --> 02:10.160
This matter

02:11.720 --> 02:13.400
I hope you all take it as a warning

02:14.800 --> 02:16.080
I will also take it as a warning

02:17.240 --> 02:18.120
Your students

02:18.800 --> 02:21.000
Will remember Your Highness's teachings
